<p>There's fantastic advice in this book. For example, most people blow off the importance of choosing the right shoes for walking. (I sure did until I had ankle and foot pain.) David has this covered along with great tips for eating healthy and how to keep the ideal food journal.</p>
  <p>There's also a week-by-week walking workout plan to help you set goals and keep your workouts organized! In addition, David shows you how to keep walking fun so you don't get burned out.</p>
